==Dutch or Frisian==
===Etymology===
From ''ien'', the Frisian word for "one", whose diminutive would be "ienje" = "small one".  (Or it could be a [[conflation]] of the first three numbers: '''ien''', twa, tri'''je''').

===Proper noun===
